---
<section class="hero" id="hero" aria-label="Hero">
  <div class="hero__bg"></div>
  <div class="hero__gradient"></div>

  <!-- Top-right chrome: orange dot only -->
  <div class="hero__chrome-top">
    <span class="accent-dot"></span>
  </div>

  <!-- Main content: headline + subhead + tags -->
  <div class="hero__content">
    <div class="hero__copy">
      <h1 class="t-display hero__headline">Choose the <span style="position:relative;display:inline-block;">future<img src="/marks/Vector-12.svg" style="position:absolute;bottom:-12px;left:-6px;width:190px;opacity:0.68;pointer-events:none;transform:rotate(1.5deg);filter:brightness(0) invert(1);" aria-hidden="true"/></span> you want. Create what matters <span style="position:relative;display:inline-block;">now.<img src="/marks/Vector-5.svg" style="position:absolute;top:-20px;left:-18px;width:145px;opacity:0.62;pointer-events:none;transform:rotate(-2.5deg);filter:brightness(0) invert(1);" aria-hidden="true"/></span></h1>
      <p class="hero__subhead">A practice to let the future you want shape how you work now, creating energized progress that expands what's possible.</p>
      <div class="tags hero__tags">
        <span class="tag">More progress</span>
        <span class="tag">Less resistance</span>
        <span class="tag">Clear direction</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>
